<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Address Changed - PropertyRent</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .change-summary {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .change-summary h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #c2410c;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .email-change {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .email-item {
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .old-email {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .new-email {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #16a34a;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .contact-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f7fafc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>PropertyRent</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Email Address Changed</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{userName}},</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>This is to inform you that the email address associated with your PropertyRent account has been successfully changed.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="change-summary">
                <h3>Email Change Summary:</h3>
                <div class="email-change">
                    <div class="email-item old-email">
                        <strong>Previous Email:</strong> This email address
                    </div>
                    <div class="email-item new-email">
                        <strong>New Email:</strong> {{newEmail}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
                    <strong>Changed on:</strong> {{formatDate}}
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <strong>üîê Security Alert:</strong> If you did not authorize this email change, your account may have been compromised. Please contact our support team immediately using the button below.
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="mailto:support@propertyrent.com" class="contact-btn">
                    Contact Support Immediately
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>All future communications will be sent to your new email address</li>
                    <li>You'll need to use your new email address to log in</li>
                    <li>This old email address is no longer associated with your account</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team at support@propertyrent.com</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyRent. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>